Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.26,0:00:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互道初次见面的时候总会有种心跳的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与人的相遇是美妙的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们要把这个瞬间当作宝物来对待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗户 什么时候打开的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着各种各样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到新的一天开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 这里是亚利亚公司 多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 多谢来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得本人想要听艾莉西亚的语音留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而特地打电话来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要妨碍我？鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是什么鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你还留着那个长鬓的话就一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了那不是鬓角了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您想预约凤尾舟的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爷很忙 没空和鬓子谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:55.12,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那份 美妙的奇迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 新威尼斯的春天就快结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我第一天到AQUA的日子算起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转眼已经快20个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以AQUA的年历来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有4个月左右就满整整一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二个夏天也就快来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟离开巢穴时 也是这种心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市就是新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是和我想像中的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是超乎我的想像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个城市 我一定会让你们看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将成为一个出色的领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 多谢来电 这里是亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我想坐艾莉西亚小姐的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何我都想坐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预约都满了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？那么其他人也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这里只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因为还是半熟手 一个人不能接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是个出色的领航员的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果不是艾莉西亚前辈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许客人也无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是去练习吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是半熟手 不能接待…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始我们就是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要喊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架啊 来人啊 救命啊 就这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这是我想出来的不让船摇晃的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是晃得很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢坐凤尾舟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不太喜欢 而且又慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个孩子是刚才打电话来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 你是从地球来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前也是住在地球上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人来的？这是不可能的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸妈妈一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和地球比起来是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有汽车 出门几乎都是用走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜也是自己去买材料回来自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟按惯例也是自己来划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是累人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很喜欢像这样全部都要自己来做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上是做不到的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告诉我你的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要坐我的凤尾舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在审问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和听说的不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子不是游客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的朋友 叫小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从地球来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是白坐船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 如你所说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点下船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个谁划得好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问谁划得好的话 当然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 请你来划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 做朋友又没什么关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 好不容易相识一场 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 蓝华 我们去看艾莉西亚前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 你真的很喜欢艾莉西亚前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是晃得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为准确的时间和愉快的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是姬屋公司的格言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA从被改造到适合人类居住已约有150年了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时至今日 被人称之为「水之星球」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而新威尼斯则以过去地球上的城市威尼斯为原型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然之间说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想有个导游会比较有趣点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你说的一点都没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对白坐船的也不用服务得如此周到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 好不容易来这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是想让她喜欢上新威尼斯再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这个城市吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初只是向往着要成为帅气的领航员才来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却越来越喜欢AQUA和新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便的交通 悠闲的时间 这些全部都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市 一定是由奇迹所构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 在曾经没有空气和水的这颗星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建造这座城市的人们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,众多回忆和思念聚集而产生出的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美妙的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的相遇也许也是奇迹之一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖烤奶油马铃薯的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤奶油马铃薯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 在家里也吃过 并不怎么喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和在地球上吃起来的感觉完全不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢 有钱却白坐船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我们也不能收她的钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马铃薯好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上卖的一般是切成小块的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃起来好像很不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 我们要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该让熟练的人来划会比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的 灯里还有秘密绝招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使出全力吧 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为灯里她在地球作练习时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴差阳错地学会了逆划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在逆划的时候她可是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样划没问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 就这样笔直过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微左边点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然采取了意外的举动 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 蓝华也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子叫小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们也做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 再见了 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 你一直想见艾莉西亚前辈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上打电话来的就是小爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说想要坐艾莉西亚前辈的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里之前 我非常讨厌AQUA和新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为之前我姐姐的新婚旅行就是来的这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年龄差得很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 所以她一直把我当小孩子对待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行回来后 就一直对我说AQUA的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我稍微有点讨厌她的夸耀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我连AQUA和新威尼斯也讨厌起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你今天为什么来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想如果实际来一次的话 也许会喜欢上这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拜托了爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他们刚带我来到这里的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都非常无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也坐过其它的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我想说 还是非得坐姐姐最为夸耀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚的凤尾舟才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却坐不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是你就决定坐灯里的凤尾舟对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天能坐上你们的船真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤奶油马铃薯非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆划也非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去后我也要向姐姐夸耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 你姐姐并不是在夸耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她是想告诉小爱AQUA上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 你想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也想告诉别人你所喜欢的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是对于你喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就想告诉姐姐今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为什么 忽然想听姐姐的闲谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了灯里你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来也许有一天 我也会喜欢上这座城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从讨厌转变成喜欢 也许是奇迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是给各位添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么道歉才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 真的今天就要离开这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想在明天的午休时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去拜托艾莉西亚前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们下次再来这里的话 我一定会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会发邮件给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次来的时候 我还想坐灯里你的凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你要尽快成为出色的领航员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 还有这个 请交给艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两位我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在凤尾舟上开始吵架的新婚夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旅行中 第一次了解到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此所不了解的讨厌的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知所措呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来和好如初了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 虽然那时候真的很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好幸福的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从讨厌转变成喜欢 虽然需要点努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能做到这点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所喜欢的人就会成为你所珍惜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所珍惜的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份奇迹 能够靠努力来获取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱的奇迹也许是靠她自己得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 想变得更喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是小爱所带来的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 今天也是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.69,0:24:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 灯里你的哪一天不是美好的一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 特别的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:32.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:42.07,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:51.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:02:02.44,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
