Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:32.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}轻拂面颊的 温柔的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:42.07,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌声中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:51.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:02:02.44,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}闭上双眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:10.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}是风的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:20.80,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}来 让我们出发 向着闪亮的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:29.96,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}脸上的笑容 从未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:40.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}快 传达到彼方 把这份感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:50.72,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}托付给清风 带到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精灵
